If you are looking for a modern hotel to stay in while visiting Rome the Una would be a good choice.	Anyone planning a trip to Rome would be well served to look at the Una as a great place to spend your vacation dollars.	If and when I go back to Rome, I will stay at the Una.	Would stay in hotel again and only wished that we had stayed in UNA Hotel in Milan on the next stop on our visit of Italy.	Overall, we would come back to this hotel, if we were to visit Rome again.